Mobility  DECARBONIZATION  & ENERGY EFFICIENCY  Wheels of progress - India  1,200 locomotives of 9,000 horsepower (HP),  including 35 years of full-service maintenance  • India rail transport and logistics networks   used daily by 24 million passengers   • Expanding railway network is tipped to grow   400% by 2030  • Creating world’s largest green rail network  • Locomotives save 800m+ tons of CO2   emissions over their lifecycle 